<volume>图形系统</volume>
<interface>IListView</interface><method> SetColumnImage </method>
    <description>
        <para>
            设置 ListView 中指定列的图片信息（该图片并不会显示在 ListView 上）。
        </para>
    </description>
    <syntax>
        <return_val> ECode </return_val>
        <parameters>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> Int32 </param_type>
                <param_name> index </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
指定列的索引值，有效值为 0～列数-1                   </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> IImage*  </param_type>
                <param_name> image </param_name>
                <param_note>
<para>
指向 <link url="../../../graphics/interface/IImage.htm">IImage</link> 接口的指针，用于获取列的图片（请先确定已经创建了该图片对象并获得了它的 <link url="../../../graphics/interface/IImage.htm">IImage</link> 接口，有关更多信息可参考：<link url="../../../graphics/class/CImage.htm">CImage 类介绍</link>）</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

<return>
    <table>
	        <th>
	    	    <td>常见返回值 </td>
	    	    <td>描述</td>
	        </th>
	        <tr>
	    	    <td>NOERROR</td>
	    	    <td>成功设置列信息</td>
	        </tr>
	        <tr>
	    	    <td>E_INVALID_ARGUMENT</td>
	    	    <td>参数无效</td>
	        </tr>
	    </table>
    <para>其它参见<link url="../../../../../../car_technology/fundamental/development_environment/car/ECode.htm">ECode</link>相关帮助。</para>
</return>
